tips.Description: It was $5.00 with bet365, TopSport, ClassicBet & Best Bookies and $4.80 with Neds, BetEasy, Ladbrokes, Unibet, BlueBet & TopBetta when first sent at 12:55pm. Promising two year old who raced against better company than this in Autumn and resumes here off a very nice trial, when not blinkered. The blinkers go on today and he will be very strong late.

It was $4.00 with bet365, Sportsbet, TopSport, BetEasy, Ladbrokes, ClassicBet, Best Bookies, Sports Betting, TAB & Ubet when first sent at 12:55pm. Relished the softer going at Sandown last start when leading all the way in very good time. Can control from the front again here.

It was $3.60 with bet365, Sportsbet, BetEasy & BlueBet and $3.50 with most of the other major bookies when first sent at 12:55pm. Up and coming sprinter who steamed down the middle of the track here last time out, when second up off a very long spell. Can only be further improved and loves the soft going.

It was $7.50 with bet365 and $6.50 with TopSport, Neds, BetEasy, Ladbrokes, BlueBet, ClassicBet, TopBetta & Best Bookies when first sent at 12:55pm. Chased home well behind the boom young sprinters Zoustyle and Plague Stone at this course last start and drawn to tag a good speed here again.

It was $4.40 with TopSport, Neds, ClassicBet & Best Bookies and $4.20 with bet365, Sportsbet, BetEasy, Ladbrokes, Unibet, BlueBet and TopBetta when first sent at 12:55pm. Quality mare who races best when her runs are spaced. Little speed here should see her get up outside the lead and be terribly tough to get past.
